Package oogasalad.editor.controller

Interface EditorController

All Known Implementing Classes:
ConcreteEditorController
public interface EditorController
Defines the primary interface for interaction between the Editor View and the Editor Model/Data. Provides methods for managing editor objects, selection, events, and listeners. Includes methods for handling prefab (BlueprintData) placement and saving.
Author:
Tatum McKinnis, Jacob You
